{"tid":2121183,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"人西+Anita Wong+渣狗真係好鍾意抹黑龍門","createTime":"2020-07-23T07:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T12:59:57.000Z","uid":4599,"like":56,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"80f8a0a573922ba89e9dc901485a29481d364481","tid":2121183,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"話說我就入咗去睇下呢班人最近有咩講啦<br />\n話晒龍門冰室真係俾到人睇到佢哋做實事<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">點知就見到佢哋咁講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAJo3eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAJo3eb.png&h=583f5f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正想笑下龍門之際，打算上網Fact Check下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">屌！點知人哋真係19星，人西群組班人究竟係未見過世面定真心想抹黑龍門？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/396mPV4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F396mPV4.png&h=a6f79186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">我只係知渣狗一出Post，呢班人就會出嚟吹奏佢哋，咁我想問其實</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">渣狗其實係咪出緊錢搵人搞龍門呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我開個Post唔係想分化，而係想以正視聽，唔係下下都入龍門冰室數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：光榮龍門fans"},{"pid":"fdaa34c68c659f6fb1bf593065f2034586ce14eb","tid":2121183,"uid":4599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"呢樣嘢真係要推，以正視聽返，唔係鳩噏就係"},{"pid":"1a7d3c1cc537ca2c4acd9e94cee45304c5de770d","tid":2121183,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:04:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22dc699bc2420b602348b61c60649f8ac6d74b85","tid":2121183,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac3b13230f2690ff629ca9251897e5f1379912a1","tid":2121183,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07: